{"id":"guide/i18n-common","title":"Common Internationalization tasks","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-common.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"common-internationalization-tasks\" translation-result=\"on\">常見的國際化任務<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common#common-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"common-internationalization-tasks\">Common Internationalization tasks<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common#common-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用 Angular 讓你的應用程式國際化</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use Angular to internationalize your application</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用內建管道以本地格式顯示日期、數字、百分比和貨幣。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use built-in pipes to display dates, numbers, percentages, and currencies in a local format.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在元件範本中標記文字以進行翻譯。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Mark text in component templates for translation.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">標記複數形式的表示式以供翻譯。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Mark plural forms of expressions for translation.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">標記替代文字以進行翻譯。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Mark alternate text for translation.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在為國際受眾準備應用程式後，使用 <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 來本地化你的應用程式。完成以下任務以本地化你的應用程式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">After you prepare your application for an international audience, use the <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> to localize your application.\nComplete the following tasks to localize your application.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用 CLI 將標記的文字提取到<em>源語言</em>檔案中。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the CLI to extract marked text to a <em>source language</em> file.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">為每種語言製作此檔案的副本，並將這些<em>翻譯檔案</em>傳送給翻譯人員或服務。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Make a copy of this file for each language, and send these <em>translation files</em> to a translator or service.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在為一種或多種語言環境建構應用程式時，使用 CLI 合併完成的翻譯檔案。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the CLI to merge the finished translation files when building your application for one or more locales.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要瀏覽本指南中使用的法語翻譯範例應用程式，請參閱<live-example></live-example> 。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To explore the sample application with French translations used in this guide, see <live-example></live-example>.</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" translation-result=\"on\">前提條件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"prerequisites\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在準備翻譯你的應用之前，你應該對以下主題有基本的瞭解。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To prepare your application for translations, you should have a basic understanding of the following subjects.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">範本</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">Templates</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">元件</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">Components</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 用於管理 Angular 開發週期的命令列工具</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> command-line tool for managing the Angular development cycle</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">Extensible Markup Language (XML)</a> 用於翻譯檔案</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">Extensible Markup Language (XML)</a> used for translation files</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"steps-to-localize-your-app\" translation-result=\"on\">本地化應用程式的步驟<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common#steps-to-localize-your-app\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"steps-to-localize-your-app\">Steps to localize your app<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common#steps-to-localize-your-app\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要本地化你的應用程式，請完成以下常規操作。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To localize your application, complete the following general actions.</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package\" title=\"Common Internationalization task #1: Add the localize package | Angular\">新增本地化套件</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package\" title=\"Common Internationalization task #1: Add the localize package | Angular\">Add the localize package</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\" title=\"Refer to locales by ID | Angular\">透過 ID 參考語言環境</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\" title=\"Refer to locales by ID | Angular\">Refer to locales by ID</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\" title=\"Format data based on locale | Angular\">根據語言環境格式化資料</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\" title=\"Format data based on locale | Angular\">Format data based on locale</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-prepare\" title=\"Prepare templates for translations | Angular\">準備翻譯範本</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-prepare\" title=\"Prepare templates for translations | Angular\">Prepare templates for translations</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-translation-files\" title=\"Work with translation files | Angular\">使用翻譯檔案</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-translation-files\" title=\"Work with translation files | Angular\">Work with translation files</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-merge\" title=\"Merge translations into the application | Angular\">將翻譯合併到應用程式中</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-merge\" title=\"Merge translations into the application | Angular\">Merge translations into the app</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-deploy\" title=\"Deploy multiple locales | Angular\">部署多個語言環境</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-deploy\" title=\"Deploy multiple locales | Angular\">Deploy multiple locales</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">當你按照操作進行操作時，<a href=\"guide/i18n-example\" title=\"Example Angular application: Explore the translated example application | Angular\">瀏覽已翻譯的範例應用程式</a>。</p><p translation-result=\"on\">在特殊情況下，需要執行以下操作。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">While you follow the actions, <a href=\"guide/i18n-example\" title=\"Example Angular application: Explore the translated example application | Angular\">explore the translated example app</a>.</p>\n\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">In special cases, the following actions are required.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果你需要設定 <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\">LOCALE_ID</a> 令牌，請<a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale\" title=\"Set the source locale manually | Angular\">手動設定源語言環境</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale\" title=\"Set the source locale manually | Angular\">Set the source locale manually</a>, if you need to set the <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\">LOCALE_ID</a> token.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\" title=\"Import global variants of the locale data | Angular\">匯入語言環境資料的全域變數</a> 以獲得額外的語言環境資料。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\" title=\"Import global variants of the locale data | Angular\">Import global variants of the locale data</a> for extra locale data.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果你需要對匹配翻譯進行更多控制，請<a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\" title=\"Manage marked text with custom IDs | Angular\">使用自訂 ID 管理標記文字</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\" title=\"Manage marked text with custom IDs | Angular\">Manage marked text with custom IDs</a>, if you require more control over matching translations.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- externla links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間： 2021/9/15</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - cli\n - guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\n - guide/glossary#component\n - guide/glossary#template\n - guide/i18n-common#common-internationalization-tasks\n - guide/i18n-common#prerequisites\n - guide/i18n-common#steps-to-localize-your-app\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package\n - guide/i18n-common-deploy\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - guide/i18n-common-merge\n - guide/i18n-common-prepare\n - guide/i18n-common-translation-files\n - guide/i18n-example\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\n - guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\n - guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-common.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://www.w3.org/XML\n-->"}